OL,3,CEx-navy officer jailed for planning to
OL,4,Crape and prostitute young girls
OL,6,FA former naval officer with the
OL,7,FCanadian Armed Forces has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor 12 years after committing 12 child
OL,9,Fsex offences.
OL,11,FBenjamin Solowan, 40 and living in
OL,12,FSark at the time of his arrest last
OL,13,FDecember, planned extreme sexual
OL,14,Factivity with girls as young as nine
OL,15,Fyears old, as well as discussing
OL,16,Fprostituting children for money and
OL,17,Fmaking indecent images of children.
