OL,3,CEx-navy officer jailed for planning to
OL,4,Crape and prostitute young girls
OL,6,FAfter the custodial sentence, he was
OL,7,Falso given several orders, including
OL,8,Ffive years on licence and told not to
OL,9,Fcontact girls under 16 without
OL,10,Fpermission from his supervising
OL,11,Fofficer.
OL,13,FSolowan was working remotely as a
OL,14,Fcomputer software engineer when he
OL,15,Fstarted talking with 'Sophie' online,
OL,16,Fbelieving she was a 12-year-old girl.
OL,18,FThe conversations quickly became
OL,19,Fsexual and many of the 87 pages of
OL,20,Fmessages were too explicit to be read
OL,21,Fout in Guernsey's Royal Court.
