OL,6,FSolowan had booked flights to meet up
OL,7,Fwith her in the UK, but Sophie was
OL,8,Factually a law enforcement officer.
OL,10,FHe was subsequently arrested in Sark
OL,11,Fon 16 December 2024 and police
OL,12,Fdiscovered extensive evidence of
OL,13,Ffurther offences on Solowan's devices
OL,14,F- including 393 pages of messages with
OL,15,Fa 14-year-old called 'Imarni', who
OL,16,Ftold him she could give him access to
OL,17,Fother children as young as nine.
