OL,10,Fmasquerading as a minor.
OL,12,FHe drew Solowan in by acting as a
OL,13,Frange of other characters within the
OL,14,Fonline chats, and Solowan responded by
OL,15,Fplanning extreme sexual activity with
OL,16,Fwhat he believed was a number of young
OL,17,Fgirls, as well as talking about
OL,18,Fprostituting them out for money.
