OL,6,FIn a letter read out in court, Solowan
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am not asking for mercy, I
OL,8,Fdeserve to be in prison and it's
OL,9,Fprobably the best place for me to be
OL,10,Fto receive the help I need."
OL,12,FIn sentencing, Judge Russell Finch
OL,13,Fstated: "The Court had to confront
OL,14,Freal evil and listen to messages which
OL,15,Fwere disgusting and disturbing in the
OL,16,Fextreme."
OL,18,FHe added he was relieved that Solowan
OL,19,Fdid not go on to carry out his sexual
OL,20,Fintentions.
